  "prompt": "Where can I find a free online course to learn WordPress themes management?",
  "response": "There are several platforms where you can find free online courses to learn WordPress theme management. Here are some options to consider:\n\n1. **Coursera**: While many courses are paid, you can often audit courses for free. Look for courses related to WordPress, web development, or website design.\n\n2. **Udemy**: Udemy has a range of free courses related to WordPress. You can filter the search results to show only free courses.\n\n3. **YouTube**: A vast resource for learning, there are many tutorials and full courses available for free. Search for terms like \"WordPress theme management tutorial.\"\n\n4. **WordPress.org**: The official WordPress website has a plethora of documentation and tutorials on using and managing themes. The \"Learn\" section might also have relevant resources.\n\n5. **LinkedIn Learning**: They offer a month of free access, where you can explore various WordPress courses, including theme management.\n\n6. **Skillshare**: Similar to LinkedIn Learning, they offer a free trial period and have courses related to WordPress themes.\n\n7. **FreeCodeCamp**: They offer comprehensive tutorials and full courses on web development topics, including managing WordPress sites and themes.\n\n8. **WP101**: They often have free introductory videos on WordPress basics, including theme management.\n\nBefore enrolling in any course, make sure to check the content previews and reviews to ensure they meet your learning needs.",
